<button class="accordion">Can sepsis come back?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>Sepsis can affect anyone at any time, but some people are at higher risk than others. There has been some research that looked at how sepsis survivors do over the long-term. Researchers have found that over the following year at least, some survivors are more prone to contracting another infection.</p>
